PrecisOrder declaring that the Governor in Council is of the opinion that it is in the national interest for the Minister of Energy, Mines and Resources to develop a project of special assistance in respect of the Hibernia Development Project and to implement the project by entering into Interest Free Loan Agreements with Mobil, Chevron and Murphy Oil.
